    text_local: "Imovina dužnika pojedinca na kojoj se ovrha protiv njega ne bi mogla provesti prema općim pravilima ovršnoga postupka ne ulazi u stečajnu masu.",
    text: "Assets of an individual debtor on which enforcement against them could not be carried out under the general rules of enforcement proceedings do not form part of the bankruptcy estate.",
