    text_local: "Podružnica prestaje:\n\n1) na osnovu odluke nadležnog organa privrednog društva;\n\n2) ako privredno društvo koje je osnovalo podružnicu prestane da postoji.",
    text: "A branch ceases: 1) by decision of the competent organ of the commercial company; 2) if the company that founded the branch ceases to exist.",
